{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-entry-js","path":"/notes/py/socket/bind","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"socket.bind"},"html":"<h3><code class=\"language-text\">socket.bind(address)</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>This function binds the socket to an address</li>\n<li>Typically, we do this to the server socket</li>\n<li>The format of <code class=\"language-text\">address</code> depends on the address family</li>\n<li>In most cases, <code class=\"language-text\">address</code> needs to be a tuple <code class=\"language-text\">(hostname, port)</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Example of <code class=\"language-text\">bind</code></h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> socket\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> sock <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> socket<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>AF_INET<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> SOCK_STREAM<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># server socket</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> addr <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">25000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>   <span class=\"token comment\"># listen on port 25000</span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>sock<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>socket<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>socket\n fd<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> proto<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n family<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>AddressFamily<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>AF_INET<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n <span class=\"token builtin\">type</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>SocketKind<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>SOCK_STREAM<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n laddr<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'0.0.0.0'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> sock<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>bind<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>addr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>sock<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>socket<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>socket\n fd<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> proto<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n family<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>AddressFamily<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>AF_INET<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n <span class=\"token builtin\">type</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>SocketKind<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>SOCK_STREAM<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n laddr<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'0.0.0.0'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">25000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>References</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://index-of.co.uk/Python/Python%20Essential%20Reference,%20Fourth%20Edition.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Python Essential Reference</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.python.org/3/library/socket.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Documentation for socket API</a></li>\n</ul>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"py/socket/bind","previousSlug":"py/socket/accept","nextSlug":"py/socket/connect","previousTitle":"socket.accept","nextTitle":"socket.connect"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}